26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_disp_outp.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:31 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "outp.h"
30
31#include <subdev/bios.h>
32#include <subdev/bios/dcb.h>
33#include <subdev/i2c.h>
34
35void
36nvkm_output_fini(struct nvkm_output *outp)
37{
38 if (outp->func->fini)
39 outp->func->fini(outp);
40}
41
42void
43nvkm_output_init(struct nvkm_output *outp)
44{
45 if (outp->func->init)
46 outp->func->init(outp);
47}
48
49void
50nvkm_output_del(struct nvkm_output **poutp)
51{
52 struct nvkm_output *outp = *poutp;
53 if (outp && !WARN_ON(!outp->func)) {
54 if (outp->func->dtor)
55 *poutp = outp->func->dtor(outp);
56 kfree(*poutp);
57 *poutp = NULL;
58 }
59}
60
61void
62nvkm_output_ctor(const struct nvkm_output_func *func, struct nvkm_disp *disp,
63 int index, struct dcb_output *dcbE, struct nvkm_output *outp)
64{
65 struct nvkm_i2c *i2c = disp->engine.subdev.device->i2c;
66
67 outp->func = func;
68 outp->disp = disp;
69 outp->index = index;
70 outp->info = *dcbE;
71 outp->i2c = nvkm_i2c_bus_find(i2c, dcbE->i2c_index);
72 outp->or = ffs(outp->info.or) - 1;
73
74 OUTP_DBG(outp, "type %02x loc %d or %d link %d con %x "
75 "edid %x bus %d head %x",
76 outp->info.type, outp->info.location, outp->info.or,
77 outp->info.type >= 2 ? outp->info.sorconf.link : 0,
78 outp->info.connector, outp->info.i2c_index,
79 outp->info.bus, outp->info.heads);
80}
81
82int
83nvkm_output_new_(const struct nvkm_output_func *func,
84 struct nvkm_disp *disp, int index, struct dcb_output *dcbE,
85 struct nvkm_output **poutp)
86{
87 if (!(*poutp = kzalloc(sizeof(**poutp), GFP_KERNEL)))
88 return -ENOMEM;
89
90 nvkm_output_ctor(func, disp, index, dcbE, *poutp);
91 return 0;
92}
